{"tid":111907,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"提好友魯芬離世眼濕濕 曾志偉：佢好有義氣鍾意幫人","createTime":"2017-02-07T17:20:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-08T15:07:34.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bb1f0d7a65187f0e7fddceef784a8f3d64c6987d","tid":111907,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T17:20:43.000Z","msg":"魯芬日前因皮肌炎導致肺部衰竭離世，代表作之一嘅《女子監獄》，由曾志偉介紹其飾演。<br />\n<br />\n今日志偉出席活動提到魯芬日前因病離世，同佢亦師亦友嘅志偉提到好友離世時眼濕濕，佢話：「其實佢自己好努力，好鍾意佢，佢好有義氣，成個男人咁，鍾意幫人，佢個造型香港冇，男人搵大傻，女人一定搵佢，兇神惡殺又得，兇神惡殺得嚟善良又得，佢走咗我都好難過，唔只係電影上嘅關係，佢同我屋企人好close，我係最早知道呢個消息，噚晚唔想講，其實好難過。」<br />\n志偉又指魯芬昏迷至離世，走得好快好快。問到演藝人協會會唔會幫忙？志偉表示委員會已同魯芬姪女聯絡，大多負責接待工作，而經濟上則唔需要幫忙，因魯芬略有積蓄。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170207/large/1486469974_6fc9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170207%2Flarge%2F1486469974_6fc9.jpg&h=ec59c3b5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"80fbe8ceb5e27cacea59c226acb3b09e5a64c131","tid":111907,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T17:51:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d75094183ba010d38c14b7bfc48e12ef29d3a691","tid":111907,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T18:50:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3e167b6a5aa6cb5dc9128747f6d65da26fcc5f8","tid":111907,"uid":44678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T01:12:08.000Z","msg":"龍咁威既大家姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b2ab7e62ae1fc1669fb1c2c8a627126d302d1eb","tid":111907,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T03:21:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\"